          <p class="welcome-line" data-line="3">calidad y acceso legal.</p>
          <p class="welcome-line welcome-line-final" data-line="4">
            <span>Bienvenido a</span>
            <img class="welcome-line-logo" src="/img/flora-logo-white.png" alt="Flora" width="1472" height="298" />
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="welcome-outro">
